widgets_values: Photograph of an East Asian woman with fair skin and long, straight black hair, standing against a plain, light gray wall. She is wearing a white, halter-neck, sleeveless dress with layered ruffles on the bodice and a voluminous, tiered skirt. The dress has a sheer, delicate texture. She accessorizes with a pearl necklace and matching pearl drop earrings. Her makeup is subtle, with a natural look and red lipstick. She has a slender build and a gentle, serene expression. The overall style is elegant and ethereal, with a focus on lightness and simplicity. The background is minimalistic, emphasizing her as the central subject.

Photograph of a young Asian woman with long, straight brown hair, fair skin, and soft pink blush on her cheeks. She is winking and smiling slightly, with her right hand touching her face. She is wearing a grey, long-sleeve, off-shoulder top that reveals black lace bra straps and a small, cut-out section of the top showing a row of black polka dots. Her breasts are moderately sized and visible through the cut-out. The background features light wooden panels and a white couch. The image has a casual, intimate feel, with a focus on the subject's playful, confident expression.
